3:10 to Yuma;;86;;89;;R;;Outlaw Ben Wade (Russell Crowe) terrorizes 1800s Arizona, especially the Southern Railroad, until he is finally captured. Wade must be brought to trial, so Dan Evans (Christian Bale), the owner of a drought-stricken ranch, volunteers to escort him to the train. Along the trail, a grudging respect forms between the men, but danger looms at every turn, and the criminal's men are in pursuit.;;Drama,Western;;James Mangold;;2007;;Russell Crowe,Christian Bale,Logan Lerman,Dallas Roberts,Ben Foster,Peter Fonda,Vinessa Shaw,Alan Tudyk,Luce Rains,Gretchen Mol;;https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/310_to_yuma